abstract: Coordinated bombings in the insurgency-plagued south of Thailand kill at least three people and wound dozens; military blames Muslim insurgent groups.
snippet: Coordinated bombings in the insurgency-plagued south of Thailand killed at least three people and wounded dozens on Tuesday.
lead_paragraph: Coordinated bombings in the insurgency-plagued south of Thailand killed at least three people and wounded dozens on Tuesday.

headline.seo: Bombings Kill 3 in South of Thailand
